# ── CAPALY Mobile — environment (LOCAL DEV ONLY) ────────────────────────────
# This .env is used only when running `expo start` on your machine. It is
# gitignored and is NOT bundled into EAS cloud builds.
#
# Point the app at your CAPALY backend:
#   - Android emulator:        http://10.0.2.2:5000/api
#   - iOS simulator:           http://localhost:5000/api
#   - Physical phone (Expo Go): your computer's LAN IP, e.g. http://192.168.1.20:5000/api
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL takes priority over app.json -> expo.extra.apiUrl.
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:5000/api
#
# ── PRODUCTION ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Built APKs/AABs do NOT read this file. The production API URL comes from:
#   1. eas.json  -> build.<profile>.env.EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL  (https://api.capaly.in/api)
#   2. app.json  -> expo.extra.apiUrl                         (https://api.capaly.in/api)
